Rivennid ecological assessment primarily concerns the Prism Thesis faction's field trials south of the Cinderteeth: implanted resonance crystals in old-growth root systems represent an unauthorized modification to the regional ecological network, propagating without oversight for centuries.
The crystal-to-root interface is technically sophisticated: the Conclave's preservation matrices interact with mycorrhizal networks, using the fungal communication system as an energy distribution medium for crystal resonance.
